txt.en: Sárgo is in Zirakazhâr.\n\nYou should return to Sárgo.

'Some of our brethren have not returned from scouting. One group was investigating Orc camps, while the other was looking into the Wargs. I fear for their safety, Hermáth. Please look for them and bring them back, if they still yet live.'
Thrain's scouts are overdue to report in. Sárgo fears the worst.
'This is fine work you have done today, friend. Those you freed owe you their life.'
Missing scouts can be found in Gadh Ujáf, Zagâf Muzug, and Rung-shakam.\n\nYou should look for, and rescue, the missing scouts.
